channel.title: Need Some Help
channel.description:
Well i have been using Jframe for a bit now and was thinking about releasing a dummy proof Admin Panel kinda like how Xent did for EasyRSC but it would be for all RSCD v25 servers
Everything now you see works... but im stuck on what else to add or improve...
When i am done i will release the full source to it.
here are some screen caps...
[img]http://img693.imageshack.us/img693/5006/screenshot1r.png[/img] [img]http://img412.imageshack.us/img412/7226/screenshot2p.png[/img] [img]http://img695.imageshack.us/img695/9784/screenshot3.png[/img] [img]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/4576/screenshot4g.png[/img] [img]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/791/screenshot5e.png[/img]
Any ideas or suggestions of what to put into it?

Also im going to add all trade and duel logs of what the person traded or staked…[/quote]

Very nice, but it will be pretty hard to make it real time view:S?
